== '''Zolm ani Bhurgeponn''' ==
Anthonicho zolm, Egyptachea doxinn' bhagant, Herakleopolis Magna, hea suvate lagsar Koma ganvant, 251 hea vorsak eka girest bhatkaranchea kuttumbhant zalo. To ottra vorsancho also tedna tachi avoi bapui hea sonvsarak ontorlim, ani tacho fuddle poramos tache ankvar bhoinin kelo. Tornnea piraer tachea mon'nant Jezuchim uttram saddlim, "Tuka sompurnn zaunchi khuxi zalear, voch, tuji lagim asa titlem-i vinkun ghoribank di, ani sorgar tuka thevo melltolo tea magir Mhgoje pattlean ie",[Mt 19:21] ani tednam tannim tim Uttrak khoreponnin pallo diun, tannim aplim bhattam xezareank dilim ani axillem titlem vinkun, dhuddu ghoribank dille ani aple bhoinink eka madrinchea conventant ghatli. Ani to devosponni gurucho xis zalo.


